---
title: Synthesis — Phase 3 (Blindspot Detection + Verdict Synthesis)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant ORC as Orchestrator
    participant REDIS as Redis Streams
    participant BS as blindspot-detector<br/>(MCP Server)
    participant SYNTH as synthesizer<br/>(MCP Server)

    Note over ORC,SYNTH: Precondition: all 5 parallel agents STOP received.<br/>Phase 3a — Blindspot Detection (pull pattern)

    ORC->>BS: MCP invoke_task({run_id, task: "analyze_blindspot"})

    BS-->>ORC: MCP tool_request: get_observations(run_id, "COVERAGE_*")

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:...:coverage-left - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: 4 observations (article_count=12, framing=SUPPORTIVE, ...)

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:...:coverage-center - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: 4 observations (article_count=8, framing=CRITICAL, ...)

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE reasoning:...:coverage-right - +
    REDIS-->>ORC: 4 observations (article_count=11, framing=CRITICAL, ...)

    ORC-->>BS: consolidated COVERAGE_* observations from all 3 agents

    BS->>BS: compute coverage asymmetry score<br/>left=12 SUPPORTIVE, center=8 CRITICAL,<br/>right=11 CRITICAL → no major blindspot

    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=synthesis
    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_SCORE, 0.12, F)<br/>publish(BLINDSPOT_DIRECTION, NONE, F)<br/>publish(CROSS_SPECTRUM_CORROBORATION, FALSE, F)
    BS->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP
    ORC->>ORC: blindspot-detector = COMPLETE

    Note over ORC,SYNTH: Phase 3b — Synthesis (pull pattern)<br/>All 9 preceding agents complete.<br/>Orchestrator assembles consolidated observation log.

    ORC->>REDIS: XRANGE all 9 agent streams<br/>collect F/C status observations

    ORC->>SYNTH: MCP invoke_task({<br/>  run_id,<br/>  consolidated_observations: [all F/C obs from all agents]<br/>})

    Note over SYNTH: Synthesizer applies DetermineOBXResolution<br/>DMN to resolve authoritative value per code.<br/>Computes weighted confidence score.

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: resolve authoritative obs per code<br/>apply confidence weights:<br/>  claimreview_match: 0.35<br/>  domain_evidence: 0.30<br/>  cross_spectrum: 0.20<br/>  blindspot_penalty: -0.10<br/>  → CONFIDENCE_SCORE = 0.31

    SYNTH->>SYNTH: map 0.31 → MOSTLY_FALSE<br/>(range: 0.25-0.44)

    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=START phase=synthesis
    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=OBS<br/>publish(CONFIDENCE_SCORE, 0.31, F)<br/>publish(VERDICT, MOSTLY_FALSE, F)<br/>publish(VERDICT_NARRATIVE, "...", F)<br/>publish(SYNTHESIS_SIGNAL_COUNT, 28, F)<br/>publish(SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON, "", F)

    Note over SYNTH: Checks if VERDICT differs from CLAIMREVIEW_VERDICT.<br/>PolitiFact said MOSTLY_FALSE. System agrees.<br/>SYNTHESIS_OVERRIDE_REASON left empty.

    SYNTH->>REDIS: XADD ... type=STOP finalStatus=F

    ORC->>REDIS: XREADGROUP — consume STOP
    ORC->>ORC: synthesizer = COMPLETE<br/>status = SYNTHESIZED

    Note over ORC: SYNTHESIZED state triggers publication.<br/>Consumer API reads finalized observations<br/>directly from Redis Streams.
